Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.63,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.91,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團為了統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以無人操縱MD\N為主要軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.89,0:01:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於反對財團的功利主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有權力被奪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.10,0:01:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織形態出現改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉著MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們快速地擴大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.41,0:02:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於宇宙衛星認同了財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團下令殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.78,0:02:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史的洪流繼續不斷倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要比任何人都戰鬥到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比地球上的任何人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.96,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比山克王國的莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.17,0:02:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十一話\N[玻璃的山克王國]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在校舍的理事長室等你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後我們自己去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不懂說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而要我說謊的角色不適合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要回鋼彈後，我就馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊!希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家需要鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.44,0:03:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，那件事一定要保密啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜不需要鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，需要它保護公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要明白，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真仁慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好少見!是男生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩人從哪個國家來的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前面的是傭人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.33,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕的保鏢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作為這所學園的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎兩位入學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛\N你沒收到學園的校服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不打算久留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成在這國家的事後\N我就離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前鋼彈駕駛員，OZ宇宙軍特士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.57,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在L2E區0X地點下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說這個人也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國也有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已得到他們協助搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以留在這國家\N直至找到他吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈駕駛員在山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不妥吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我無必要故意誇口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但躲躲藏藏，問題也不會解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，這個國家沒有戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡也是一個普通男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心讚賞妳這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變命運的英明決斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向各位介紹兩位新朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是卡特爾‧拿巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.80,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流星作戰，終於開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會隨時和你聯絡告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊的目標和敵人的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，你就從速行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，給你取個代號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定借用宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平領導人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希洛‧唯，多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為男孩認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是靠對話不能解決一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是男女的分別吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女性也有喜歡戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不介意\N可以做我的對手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽過你的自我介紹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我還未自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫桃樂絲‧卡塔羅尼亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和羅姆斐拉的幹部有血緣關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但莉莉娜殿下接納我為同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想和你做好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我不可以不堅強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你討厭吧，軟弱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.16,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某地方有一個和你同名的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人為了令宇宙得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豁出性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後成為宇宙的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許多人因為他的死而悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.34,0:07:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憤而發誓要報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.24,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一個同名的人\N也正在成為傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有最高天份和力量的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.42,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也會為和平而戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.19,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也會為了\N變成傳說而喪命吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的騎士不會故意打輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了躲藏而輸給女性這等事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堅強、高尚、猛烈地燃燒生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後才步向死亡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該能創造更偉大的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.14,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然厲害\N但是，我也很了得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白妳說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來還有兩個希洛‧唯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打算隱瞞身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣\N我們永遠一起在山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳召喚我嗎?莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才，羅姆斐拉來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請求批準在山克王國內戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼回事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被OZ追殺的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃進了南部的森林地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才已經叫他們馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們離開，能逃得掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們好像有傷兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也可以向敵人投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是本國的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有傷兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉的追擊部隊正在迫近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去命令特列斯派的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退到國境之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.03,0:09:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.00,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能讓他們暫時投奔本國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，羅姆斐拉也會停止攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也知道羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.48,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當山克王國是眼中釘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不能把傷兵交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想為了避免混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出違反人道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳明白，諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就那樣和特列斯派聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N想不到要逃進山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新生OZ的攻擊好巧妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被迫至走投無路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然被羅姆斐拉利用\N為攻擊山克王國的藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，我們不能慢吞吞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續下去會為這國家帶來麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!以你的身體狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你離開不了國境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是為了不沾污\N特列斯派的聲譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定要離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，山克王國有聯絡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說莉莉娜公主有指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王國的近衛兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路克蕾琪亞‧諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國準備暫時收容各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位遵照公主的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除武裝投奔本國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信那是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊內有很多傷兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來我們樂於接受你們的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們被趕進這裡是個陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ不會就此了事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷阱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們截斷退路之後卻不來進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該輕易就能消滅我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們正要求增援部隊前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥無可避免會牽連山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.94,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，我們一定要離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡有很多\N和平主義國家的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ最近的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是想藉著在本國發動戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令和平主義國家感到不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打亂各國的團結   我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終不能為了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令山克王國出現弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主的好意我心領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進一步的情報\N也會令你們有麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想終止通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後交給我們處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，祝各位好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒我，為了這國家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!這是為了未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵的機動戰士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國再度來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.24,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐嚇他們吧   不要緊\N接過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容投奔本國的特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你們進一步入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會直接向財團抗議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.65,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我收到的情報有若干不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派為了逃過我們的追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.86,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔據了山克王國的中心部躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他們進入市區前攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們給予和平的協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派沒有攻擊的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已經那樣表明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們表明了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們更加不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有可能被敵人偷聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能這樣\N請收回承命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把特列斯派趕進市區增加傷亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.45,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴露和平主義的不設防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自私自利\N帕根，我要去現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快點準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.71,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險的\N請莉莉娜小姐三思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要直接去制止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現場有戰鬥很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新生OZ會令那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成煉獄般的地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.32,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道他們為了甚麼發動戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說我是他們的目標呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有甚麼結果也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在重要的是制止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下!快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主義國家不可以有的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把宇宙用機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改良為陸戰用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主知道這件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有這種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類才會想要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.83,0:14:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們想緊緊抱著\N玻璃手工藝般脆弱的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定會那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在才一定要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的行動\N一定對山克王國有益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們用這些陶拉斯追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我去準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝置完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.79,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然不能從這國家撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降下的MD果然是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我們趕進山克王國的中心部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上把本部隊的一切炸毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你們既然打算\N為了這國家而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的性命就還有一點用處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的用處?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們打算保護這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不設防的國家吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.46,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒剩下多少的軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想向羅姆斐拉反擊\N那就跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順利的話，或許能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.74,0:16:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這國家對我有恩，只是那樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，派兩三人跟我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!你相信他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有多少人認為\N能打贏MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是羅姆斐拉害怕的那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N那少年是鋼彈駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比想像中更沒趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，部份特列斯派已經被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但推測本隊前去市區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上轉為追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來歷不明飛機正急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是對空戰，我們暫時有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下妳曾見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的戰場嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不大想踏上戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為人會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，戰鬥的人是拼命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得那方面好有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的會好緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想感謝出生於這時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些白色機體是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屬於哪個國家的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來歷不明的機動戰士運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正衝過來   甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向MD發出指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.25,0:18:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!擊落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…?   鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.18,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!桃樂絲!停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，沒事吧?  桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國不需要這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下妳會那樣說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但羅姆斐拉的行動\N正逐漸形成壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我違反了莉莉娜殿下妳的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.65,0:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為沒防衛力量會被擊敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這全是我的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願接受任何處分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.83,0:20:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不用反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和羅姆斐拉財團正面戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這程度的戰鬥力實在太少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以坐以待斃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像過去的領導人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.64,0:20:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的思想是夢想\N還是錯誤呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團會陸續消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妨礙他們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙衛星，鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳已經成為代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要戰鬥消滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，拒絕戰鬥的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.77,0:20:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形成財團現在的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代急速改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉的焦急\N是這場戰爭的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界正朝著那方向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也要明白諾茵的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在須要防衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了能擁有討論的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!你去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜索特洛瓦的人情我已經還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會照自己的意思行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的腦內沒有和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.56,0:21:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈是為了戰鬥而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會怎樣管治山克王國?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和諾茵一樣，創立防衛部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最能抗衡羅姆斐拉的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，諾茵小姐，我批準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請照你們的意思行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我和我身邊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能意見一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能令全世界有同一想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我終有一日會找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.19,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼驅使大家戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.04,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她絕對不是輸給鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.11,0:22:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我好喜歡莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.00,0:22:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.50,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.00,0:23:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.00,0:23:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.19,0:23:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.73,0:23:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球的希洛和卡特爾以外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.13,0:23:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈駕駛員停留在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.17,0:23:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ迫近躲起來繼續抵抗的迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.47,0:23:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在調整中的鋼彈地獄死神面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.54,0:23:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛翼零式展開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.58,0:23:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那場戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.01,0:23:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐對飛翼零式的性能抱有某疑問
